&lt;li&gt;Creates safe workholding methods and plans for work coordinates or tooling before any machine operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up, operation and programing of a wide range of component sizes&lt;s&gt; &lt;/s&gt;to deliver parts to meet internal deadlines or quality requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
