&lt;li&gt;Oversee leadership development, performance management, and career progression frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure strong leadership capability at all levels — with particular focus on manager effectiveness and VP/Sr. Director bench strength&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
